data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: STEP1:- Connect Red & Black cable to the power supply at Red at (+) and Balck (-). The other end of these cables connect to fixture. STEP2:- Connect BNC cable to CRO at Channel 1. (Other end of BNC cable will be used during testing) STEP3:- Place the MMB board on the fixture into the respective matching guiding pin. STEP4:- Connect J10 ribbon cable to the J10 connector & J2 ribbon cable to the J2 connector & Programming cable to J18 on the MMB DUT board. STEP5:- Connect Ethernet cable between MMB fixture and Test PC. STEP6:- Connect USB cable end of the "USB Blaster" & UART CABLE to USB ports of Test PC . STEP7:- Close the fixture by pushing the front handle toward back side
